high_descs: Walk forward past the corner of the couch then turn right and walk to the coffee table then turn right to face the couch.
Pick up the box from the couch.
Turn around and walk to the TV then turn left and walk to the table in the corner.
Turn on the lamp that is on the table.
anns.task_desc: Look at a box under the light of a lamp.

high_descs: Turn left, hang a right to the white chair, head right to the coffee table and face the gray couch on the right.
Pick up the cardboard box from the right side of the couch.
Turn around, hang a left at the television stand and walk to the small wooden table in the corner ahead.
Turn on the small lamp on the table.
anns.task_desc: Examine a box by the light of a small lamp.

high_descs: Walk to the left and navigate around the right end of the white couch until you are standing in front of it facing the cushion farthest to the right.
Pick up the open cardboard box sitting on the white couch.
turn around and walk to the TV stand, then turn left and walk to the square wood table that has a lamp sitting on it.
Turn on the lamp with the square white shade that is sitting on the wooden table.
anns.task_desc: Carry a cardboard box to a wooden end table and turn on the lamp.
